# .config - Luth's Opinonated DevEnv

# Core

## Tools

- Package Manager         ([Homebrew](https://brew.sh/))
- Terminal                ([iTerm2](https://iterm2.com/))
- Shell                   ([fish](https://fishshell.com/))
- Editor                  ([Neovim](https://neovim.io/))
- Container Runner        ([Docker](https://docker.com))
- Container Orchestration ([Kubernetes](https://kubernetes.io/))
- Version Control         ([Git](https://git-scm.com/))
- Stacked Diffs Helper    ([Graphite](https://graphite.dev/))
- AWS CLI                 ([aws/aws-cli](https://github.com/aws/aws-cli))
- AWS Vault               ([99designs/aws-vault](https://github.com/99designs/aws-vault))

## Database Vendors

- PostgreSQL ([PostgreSQL](https://postgresql.org))
- MySQL      ([MySQL](https://dev.mysql.com))

## Languages

- Golang     ([golang](https://go.dev/))
- TypeScript ([typescript](https://typescriptlang.org/))

### Golang

- Compiler                 ([go](https://formulae.brew.sh/formula/go#default))
- Linter                   ([golangci/golangci-lint](https://github.com/golangci/golangci-lint))
- Formatter                ([gofmt](https://pkg.go.dev/cmd/gofmt))
- Language Server Protocol ([gopls](https://pkg.go.dev/golang.org/x/tools/gopls))

### TypeScript

- Compiler                 ([Rollup](https://rollupjs.org/))
- Linter                   ([ESLint](https://eslint.org/))
- Formatter                ([Prettier](https://prettier.io/))
- Language Server Protocol ([typescript-language-server/typescript-language-server](https://github.com/typescript-language-server/typescript-language-server))
- Package Manager 1        ([npm](https://npmjs.com/))
- Runtime 1                ([node](https://nodejs.org/en/))
- Package Manager 2        ([bun](https://bun.sh/))
- Runtime 2                ([bun](https://bun.sh/))

